pub fn is_same_object<'other_local_1, 'other_local_2, O, T>(
        &self,
        ref1: O,
        ref2: T,
    ) -> Result<bool>
    where
        O: AsRef<JObject<'other_local_1>>,
        T: AsRef<JObject<'other_local_2>>,
    {
        Ok(jni_unchecked!(
            self.internal,
            IsSameObject,
            ref1.as_ref().as_raw(),
            ref2.as_ref().as_raw()
        ) == sys::JNI_TRUE)
    }
